# The plugin ships as text that Claude Code reads on every platform, and
# `build-plugin.mjs` writes LF. Without this, a Windows checkout rewrites every
# file to CRLF and `git status` reports the whole tree as modified after a build
# — which buries the one file that genuinely changed and makes "does the build
# reproduce the commit?" impossible to answer at a glance.
* text=auto eol=lf
